Show HN: ShowGPT – share prompts, conversations, and templates with ChatGPT
text:
I'm excited to announce the launch of showGPT, a new community for sharing all things chatGPT.

showGPT allows you to: easily share prompts and examples of conversations that you had with chatGPT, save your conversations with a convenient Chrome extension, try other people's conversations and prompts, get points on a leaderboard if other people try your prompts.

Additionally, you can create and share reusable templates and forms to make it easier to use chatGPT in a variety of ways.
